<subSubSection id="24CB1080FFB8FFE6FAB2AE6D82DFFE4A" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="6C6E430BFFB8FFE6FAB2AE6D82DFFE4A" blockId="12.[151,1437,151,430]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB8FFE6FAB2AE6D815EFEF9" bold="true" box="[199,315,259,285]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previous records from the coast of São Paulo include Iguape, Ilha Comprida, and Cananéia (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB8FFE6FF4AAE6D815CFEA5" author="Barbieri, E. &amp; Melo, G. A. S." pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="654 - 659" refId="ref53539" refString="Barbieri, E. &amp; Melo, G. A. S. (2006) Biodiversidade: ocorrencia da especie exotica Litopenaeus vannamei (Boone, 1931) no complexo estuarino-lagunar de Cananeia-Iguape-Ilha Comprida. O Mundo da Saude, 30 (4), 654 - 659. https: // doi. org / 10.20950 / 1678 - 2305.2016 v 42 n 2 p 479" type="journal article" year="2006">Barbieri &amp; Melo 2006</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB8FFE6FB32AE498255FEA6" author="Barbieri, E. &amp; Coa, F. &amp; Rezende, K. F. O." box="[327,560,295,322]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="479 - 485" refId="ref53607" refString="Barbieri, E., Coa, F. &amp; Rezende, K. F. O. (2016) The exotic species Litopenaeus vannamei (Boone, 1931) occurrence in Cananeia, Iguape and Ilha Comprida lagoon estuary complex. Boletim do Instituto de Pesca, 42 (2), 479 - 485. https: // doi. org / 10.20950 / 1678 - 2305.2016 v 42 n 2 p 479" type="journal article" year="2016">
Barbieri 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB8FFE6FBD8AE498187FEA5" box="[429,482,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName id="ABD13888FFB8FFE6F833AE498323FEA4" baseAuthorityName="Boone" baseAuthorityYear="1931" box="[582,838,295,320]" class="Malacostraca" family="Penaeidae" genus="Litopenaeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vannamei">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB8FFE6F833AE498323FEA4" box="[582,838,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Litopenaeus vannamei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is native from Eastern Pacific (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB8FFE6FECEAE498504FEA5" author="Holthuis, L. B." box="[1211,1377,295,321]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 271" refId="ref64916" refString="Holthuis, L. B. (1980) FAO Species catalogue, Vol. 1. Shrimps and prawns of the world. An annotated catalogue of species of interest to fisheries. FAO Fisheries Synopsis, 125 (1), 1 - 271." type="journal article" year="1980">Holthuis 1980</bibRefCitation>
) and was introduced in 
<collectingCountry id="14C6039BFFB8FFE6FB1DAE2581C9FE81" box="[360,428,331,357]" name="Brazil" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Brazil</collectingCountry>
as a cultivated species in shrimp farming (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB8FFE6F9E6AE2584E7FE81" author="Silva, E. D. &amp; Barros, F." box="[915,1154,331,357]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="326 - 344" refId="ref78373" refString="Silva, E. D. &amp; Barros, F. (2011) Macrofauna bentonica introduzida no Brasil: lista de especies marinhas e dulcicolas e distribuicao atual. Oecologia Australis, 15 (2), 326 - 344. https: // doi. org / 10.4257 / oeco. 2011.1502.10" type="journal article" year="2011">Silva &amp; Barros 2011</bibRefCitation>
). Records presented here refer to individuals collected in natural environment. Sequence accession number (GenBank): CCDB 5844—16S (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FFB8FFE6FAEAAEFD8143FE49" box="[159,294,403,429]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/OM720043" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">OM720043</accessionNumber>
), COI (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FFB8FFE6FB0DAEFD8199FE4A" box="[376,508,403,430]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/OM672408" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">OM672408</accessionNumber>
) (present study).
</paragraph>
